    "itemType": "journalArticle",
    "title": "The Trouble with \u1f10\u03c0\u03b9\u03c6\u03ad\u03c1\u03b5\u03c4\u03bf: Basil\u2019s <i>Hexaemeron</i> 2.6 in Context",
